SR_05_TRANSAC_METHOD_DETERMIN: Schuyler Health Foundation holds an annual capital fund raising campaign to benefit Schuyler Hospital. Each year those funds are released to Schuyler Hospital as the purpose of the funds is met. In 2018 Schuyler Health Foundation transferred $257,230 for purchase of equipment, SNF Wardrobe updates, and supplies for ADL (Activities of Daily Living) training.

NAME: SCHUYLER HEALTH FOUNDATION INC

NAME: SCHUYLER HEALTH FOUNDATION INC
SR_05_TRANSAC_METHOD_DETERMIN: Schuyler Health Foundation reimburses Schuyler Hospital for expenses paid on their behalf. These expenses include the associated costs of office space and a copier/scanner/fax. Expenses are reconciled and reimbursed on a monthly basis. For 2018 total reimbursements to Schuyler Hospital amounted to $77,779

NAME: SCHUYLER HEALTH FOUNDATION INC
